::Prowl/Annihilator/Killer::

Prowl growls as he recieves Liono's message. He reluctantly stands up, 
putting out a hand to help Iron Raptor. He looks at her, longing plainly 
written in his eyes. Love or not, though, they had to get back to base. He 
sighs.

"Let's go. Liono wants us back at the Ark," he says to Iron Raptor.

An ugly voice sounds from behind Prowl.

"You're not going anywhere .... Except for the pit." Annihilator say, aiming 
his gun at Prowl's back.

Prowl spins around, firing an acid pellet into Annihilator's shoulder before 
the pred could respond.

Killer walks out from the other side of the two maximals, launcher ready, 
"Allright," he says calmly, "We're going to do this my way. Put down your 
weapons and no one gets hurt ... for now."
